  "source_url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222898286189",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ed5a6e3-7e3d-4122-9851-c62be05627ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7ba6c521-0389-4c50-8071-f2b714a3f2d4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-93893edc-98f6-47c3-a60c-79decb756de2\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 18</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d7588417-6db8-4bd1-8111-7791c82b14c3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1d90e621-855d-432b-a017-47d2227b6661\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-adc5f85f-8de2-4181-8745-2dbfcc82335d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e39eef58-a2c3-4273-af8f-d1bb52e3d2dd\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-61298861-82ac-4fdc-a69c-4e17361a8b99\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f541affa-995f-4c1a-ba97-96fa74027fb9\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 후가공(후공정)은 인쇄 후 자신이 원하는 모양으로 만들기 위한 작업입니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-21b7bfff-2271-4268-9382-37ac9994f7a6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0393de36-660c-473c-aa61-c0bfac255729\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-10ed3aa9-78d6-45c2-a7fe-167e39437390\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ffb2d73c-7ec2-4ff2-9cf9-c78e9efa7147\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0a7751a3-8f5e-428c-8164-de7668fd36b9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c646840b-812c-4c77-882e-fc6d11927156\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>블로그 성공의 두번째는 컨텐츠의 진실함입니다. 저는 90일 동안 진심의 마음으로 글을 쓰겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d1adb1f5-8302-4670-ab38-e72ff6e185bf\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8e912c8-4195-402c-87e9-a0d05b44e11d\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a8594c29-c22d-4d0a-b241-57ad7c61d6eb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb167258-d6ee-499f-978e-677b4ff1e5cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8e8d5304-3763-4350-9e32-1033e347059c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후가공의 종류 Part2</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6b86218-a86a-4181-b988-ae9dbe4d67ac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-68ca6806-6e3d-41ba-ac64-5a0d31657033\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-78786aa7-5984-4f8b-8f57-115ef63796c0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">후가공은 자신이 최종적으로 만들고 싶은 결과물을 고민해야 합니다. 후가공은 비용이 많이 발생 할 수 있기 때문에 비용대비 효과적인 측면을 고려해야 합니다. 그래야 우리가 가장 중요하게 생각하는 가성비를 맞출수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-556bd855-36bd-4f65-8722-47e7b9ea12a2\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-80f13564-cc65-4a32-9a54-282bbfe31c6b\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-d4da9478-6e3f-44f2-8168-423a7b6ef16c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb117395-9683-4f12-a9d2-bc5c20f36794\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f89d6acf-6435-4128-9381-d32c31b29006\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7b9ce0ce-3ce7-4e89-9500-31cd8f9e6afe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>오시</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-33e146a3-2de9-4b84-8211-7c32bb4bdeb3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7b2df3bf-edcd-4745-8711-730c785e892a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d6f68fee-f524-44d4-b035-25ecbd52d495\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-33dc40bb-f57d-4441-a460-d96dd8a23dce\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">오시는 한국인쇄용어로 누름자국이라고 표시합니다. 다시 말해 오시는 인쇄물의 접어야 되는 부분이 잘 접히도록 압력을 가하는 후가공입니다. 인쇄물을 접을 때 그냥 접으면 인쇄물의 결로 인해 주름이 발생하게 되는데 깔끔하게 점기 위해 오시를 먼저 선행작업으로 하는경우가 많습니다. 특히 접지 시 평량 150g이상의 두꺼운 용지는 오시를 주어야 터지거나 갈라지지 않고 잘 접힙니다. 기본 오시 가공은 수직과 수평으로 종이를 가로지르는 가공만 가능합니다. 자유 모양으로 오시를 넣으려면 톰슨으로 작업해야하며 기본 오시는 선으로만 표시됩니다.  무선제본의 경우 책 표지가 잘 접게 펼치기 위해  풀 붙은 부분과 책날개는 제본기에서 자동으로 오시가 들어갑니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7ccd9dc1-e76f-4f82-bb18-26a8a572338f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5ec2f385-d7a3-4163-8e40-655ff973b041\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-77d88e80-c95d-4af4-8f4e-ded3bb74a35e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222898286189/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b457e1e6-7f29-4eea-a6d7-2c16a3f08c4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c0557604-6ac6-48f4-8e95-17baa618121b\" style=\"\">오시</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b164a7f9-3be2-4a36-847c-aa8693aafd19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ee2095b0-f7be-455a-9d0a-abab7a6579c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-88e052fb-bce7-4b8d-adf2-ef0fe9e00ecc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e8ee9d26-74b7-4da2-ba51-2e01e12be0e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a37a734c-f092-4ebb-b53e-df18aba1d044\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-e54da92b-6e25-4040-93ca-b4f04d0488ca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d4dd0f92-1548-4709-8666-50452338cc77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-446e7dfa-1fec-4a39-9e62-0020296a5b19\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cb936574-74d9-44b2-9593-2743908d780b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>미싱</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9cc33dc5-c2f8-44f6-b071-71f5cc4a2229\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-76b799af-ee33-4afd-867f-defd87045e5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d6d595c1-dfdf-43be-b7d0-120e3ecce3bf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5b5023f3-3089-4601-8596-8f511bbb8661\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">미싱은 종이를 손으로 쉽게 잘라낼 수 있도록 특정 영역에 선에 맞추어 점선으로 구멍을 뚫어 놓는 후가공입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1dbfdaf3-0c12-40aa-b235-54d8184061b2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fa5686a6-15fb-414a-b463-6560f3141ff3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">미싱으로 처리된 부분은 쉽게 뜯어낼 수 있어 주로 공연, 행사용 티켓, 상품권이나 쿠폰 등에 많이 사용되며, 간혹 접지가 잘 되게 하기 위해 사용하기도 합니다. 미싱도 수직과 수평으로만 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fcde6e73-c9f8-404c-b0a0-23d458e3b4cb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-93fa2dd9-9b95-44d9-8cfa-64f5f8122ce9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16407d33-2a46-4bc7-ba02-54847761e024\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222898286189/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff9913be-9fd9-4362-853e-8ef29bca5f35\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cc1ad877-dae7-4ea4-8bf4-57771c7f0fd5\" style=\"\">미싱</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9a955985-b625-4b7a-a49c-d0b4feb1afc6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c1081590-dee1-497c-882e-e764df8ab0b3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8144e9e4-63fc-4f82-86ae-fc48304cebe8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-90f00683-8b70-4fb3-9d57-0c3cfc4bfc1d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-86cd4046-4f84-4a2f-a408-b8829133c26d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-e5061ee5-9166-4980-813d-f0ae8f0d1b03\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b24cf69-46f1-402b-8a5b-1428569d4db6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-57abb786-5ca1-42b0-821a-29335f068171\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5dda23de-9d90-429e-bd42-b58956eb25da\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>타공</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3212c520-fa3f-4835-9296-b678bd44f299\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e9373ca9-83b4-4fbc-9092-f9a41cd80c1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-31a27213-1441-4ea2-87d9-eb6f2615d207\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2d2cc805-0e11-4f09-8af3-068eca32b6a4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">타공은 종이에 원형의 구멍을 뚫는 후가공입니다. 상품 택이나 라벨 등 인쇄물에 고리를 꿰어야 하는 경우나  스프링제본 시 스프링이 들어가는 부위에 구멍을 내야하는 경우 사용되는 후가공입니다. 타공의 구멍크기는 용도에 맞게 조절할 수 있습니다. 주로 스프링 제본, 다이어리, 바인더 책자 및 명함, 의류용, 상품용 Tag 등에 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b0c3379f-cb55-4a77-b441-eba5e70e2396\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c623f5bf-52e3-42d9-8a2c-3cb837fed0f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aaf904ed-57ef-4529-acf8-b277e3d77adb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:709px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222898286189/